---
title: Creamy Pesto & Leek Spaghetti with Baby Leaves & Parmesan Cheese
description: Twirl your way to happiness with this spaghetti feast! Loaded with all your favourite greens, a velvety pesto sauce, and topped with a shower of grated Parmesan cheese, it’s a pasta dish that’s as comforting as it is crave-worthy.

